(define/contract (count num1 num2 min_sum max_sum)
  (-> string? string? exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  
  (define (digit-sum n)
    (if (= n 0)
        0
        (+ (modulo n 10) (digit-sum (quotient n 10)))))

  (define (count-good-integers start end count)
    (if (> start end)
        count
        (let ((sum (digit-sum start)))
          (if (and (>= sum min_sum) (<= sum max_sum))
              (count-good-integers (+ start 1) end (modulo (+ count 1) 1000000007))
              (count-good-integers (+ start 1) end count)))))

  (count-good-integers (string->number num1) (string->number num2) 0))
